Celebrate women’s day in style with a memorable evening at The Raviz Calicut, located in the bustling heart of the city. Have it your way and your pace, whether it is a mindful moment by the pool, the pulsating vibes of the sports-themed bar, and the sumptuous dinner spread that will spoil you for choice. And to top it off, a special offer awaits every woman who walks into the most hip joint in town!
